@startuml
title Contract Declares, Runtime Enforces

' ===============================
' Shared Style
' ===============================
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

top to bottom direction

skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 8
  BorderColor #1F2937
  FontColor #111827
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color #374151
  Thickness 1.5
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #F9FAFB
  BorderColor #9CA3AF
  FontColor #374151
}

' ===============================
' Responsibility Domains
' ===============================

rectangle #E0E7FF "API Contract\n\n\
- OpenAPI schema\n\
- Semantic validation declarations\n\
- Persistence intent" as C

rectangle #DBEAFE "API Runtime\n\n\
- Interprets contract\n\
- Executes semantic validations\n\
- Applies deterministic derivations\n\
- Persists to the Database" as R

rectangle #DCFCE7 "Database Persistence\n\n\
- Durable facts recorded\n\
- Database guarantees applied\n\
- Change becomes observable" as DB

rectangle #F3E8FF "Validation Function Library\n\n\
- Pure validation functions\n\
- Reusable across contracts\n\
- Side-effect free" as V

C --> R : declared intent
R --> DB : persist to database
R --> V : invokes

note right of DB
Persistence marks the end
of runtime responsibility.
end note

@enduml
